title: MAUI Hack Day - Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane + ONLINE
thumbnailDescription: MAUI Hack Day - Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane + ONLINE
presenterName: Matt Goldman, Brady Stroud, Sam Basu, Jack Pettit & more
eventShortDescription:
​MAUI Hack Days (previously Xamarin Hack Days) are community-run events for .NET MAUI developers or people who want to learn MAUI for free.

There will be something for everyone. Experienced .NET MAUI developers can share ideas with other experienced developers. If you’re a beginner, then there’s plenty to learn on the day.
